Why Sigh No More (Mumford & Sons) best matches
- Vocal immediacy and phrase focus: The candidate 1 description highlights close‑miked, vocal‑forward performance and phrase‑forward arrangements that are lyric‑centric. That directly aligns with my priority for close, intimate lead vocals with revealed breath and phrasing, and with concise parts that serve the singer.
